description:
This is a 15 minute workout called 'Guided Mindfulness Meditation - Go Easy on Yourself - Self-care and Self-Love (15 Minutes)' from the channel MindfulPeace.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is a new guided mindfulness meditation focused on caring for yourself and showing love for yourself - GO EASY on yourself! I'll bet you are the kind of person who takes on big challenges and puts a lot of pressure on yourself. As the saying goes, we are often our own worst critics. Meditating and being mindful of what pressures cause us stress and anxiety can lead to a healthier mental state. Although it can be healthy to hold ourselves to a high standard, we don't want to work ourselves into a loss of personal well-being.

Let the dialogue and ambient music soundtrack guide you. The calm and peaceful guided meditation dialogue lasts for about 12 minutes, followed by a few minutes of ambient music to bring you back out of meditation - 15 minutes total. You really can take it EASY on yourself!
